{"tid":443541,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]Daddy今個禮拜又可以出街食飯啦","createTime":"2017-10-21T15:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T19:02:37.000Z","uid":57035,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9e6eb5df2c5acd4d3aec18b2c5f57ad626b9d7","tid":443541,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:55:53.000Z","msg":"摩連奴：輸波才出街食飯<br />\n<br />\n被問到如周六第100場主場比賽勝出的話，會否與家人外出晚宴慶祝時，摩佬有趣回應：「正好相反，如果我輸波，我會外出；如果勝出，我不會外出，這已似是一家人的事，我不會因為輸掉一場比賽而躲起來，留在家中令家人更不開心，當一個人已經做到最好，像我經常所做一樣，即使輸掉了，也不用逃避。」"},{"pid":"bcb7043f35bd87fb9f57dfaa6a5ee3be1c05288a","tid":443541,"uid":31752,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158c47f4a7b3f2a91adc58e98412ffda1c866976","tid":443541,"uid":7940,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/000823_83d2b7b2daee42fd4b31883b566c445f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F000823_83d2b7b2daee42fd4b31883b566c445f.jpg&h=3fa4fcc6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6d0771a0657ada515746c542f2903fbbfc365795","tid":443541,"uid":4004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f726b4841a3f7275f4e11da17b10b2942aa46a","tid":443541,"uid":54000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"So9Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bbe9720f42d9aa13626819